column5: I have a Navionics chip for sale for all of Lake of The Woods and the Winnipeg River System north up to the White Dog Dam. Anyone interested, please post a return message. $90.00 US
What model is it? I may be interested.

This is the number on the chip. US647XL. On the south end it starts just to the north of Green Bay and includes all of Lake Superior, Lake of the Woods up to the White Dog Dam and all water in between. If you would share a fax number or e-mail address with me, I will fax/e-mail you the maps and names of the Lakes.
If you still have it for sale, pls fax me at 204-985-5369 and include your e-mail address. Thx
